## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="47894-102">の<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs>インスタンスは、 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>オブジェクトがイベントを<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.EmulateRecognizeCompleted>発生させたときに作成されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="47894-102">An instance of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs> is created when the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> object raises the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.EmulateRecognizeCompleted> event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="47894-103">認識の結果に関する情報を取得するには<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A> 、イベントのハンドラーのプロパティにアクセスします。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="47894-103">To obtain information about the result of recognition, access the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A> property in the handler for the event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="47894-104">エミュレーションは、音声認識エンジンへの入力ではなく、音声ではなくテキストを使用するプロセスです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="47894-104">Emulation is the process by which text, instead of audio, is the input to a speech recognition engine.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="47894-105">エミュレーション中に<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>オブジェクトのオーディオ入力をバイパスするには、 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.SetInputToNull%2A>メソッドを使用します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="47894-105">To bypass the audio inputs for a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> object during emulation, use the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.SetInputToNull%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="47894-106">音声認識エンジンが認識操作<xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A>中に例外を検出した場合、プロパティは例外<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A>に設定され、プロパティはに`null`設定されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="47894-106">If the speech recognition engine encounters an exception during the recognition operation, the <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs.Error%2A> property is set to the exception and the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A> property is set to `null`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="47894-107"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs> は、<xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs> から派生します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="47894-107"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs> derives from <xref:System.ComponentModel.AsyncCompletedEventArgs>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="47894-108">次の例では、 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.EmulateRecognizeCompleted>イベントのイベントハンドラーを<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>に追加します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="47894-108">The following example adds an event handler for the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.EmulateRecognizeCompleted> event to a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="47894-109">ハンドラーは、 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A>プロパティから認識されたテキストを取得します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="47894-109">The handler gets the recognized text from the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs.Result%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
  
private SpeechRecognitionEngine sre;  
  
// Initialize the speech recognition engine.   
private void Initialize()  
{  
  sre = new SpeechRecognitionEngine();  
  
  // Add a handler for the EmulateRecognizeCompleted event.  
  sre.EmulateRecognizeCompleted += new EventHandler<EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs>(sre_EmulateRecognizeCompleted);  
  
  // Add other initialization code here.  
}  
  
// Handle the EmulateRecognizeCompleted event.   
void sre_EmulateRecognizeCompleted(object sender, EmulateRecognizeCompletedEventArgs e)  
{  
  if (e.Result == null) return;  
  
  string phrase = e.Result.Text;  
  
  // Add event handler code here.  
}  
  
```
